query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(k mk t) NoHashJoin(it2 k kt mi_idx mk t mi) NoMergeJoin(it2 k kt mi mi_idx mk t it1) */ select min(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
min(t.title) AS north_european_dark_production
from keyword AS k
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IS NOT NULL AND k.keyword IN ('violence',
'tv-special',
'10,000-mile-club',
'toronto-ontario-canada')
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2005
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info < '7.1'
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating'
inner join kind_type AS kt
on kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('video game',
'tv series')
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('USA',
'Germany',
'Norway',
'Bulgaria',
'Norwegian',
'Swedish',
'America',
'Sweden',
'Denmark',
'Canada')
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries';
